With intense action sequences, stunning visuals, and deeper exploration of Peter Parker’s legacy, Spider-Man 4 will be the next step in a new chapter of the Spider-Man universe.

snippet.title: Stranger Things - Season 5 Volume 2 Teaser Trailer | NETFLIX | 25 December, 2025
snippet.description:
#netflix #strangerthings5 #strangerthings 

Watch the 'FAN (CONCEPT) Trailer Concept' For Stranger Things - Season 5 (2025) (More Info About This Video Down Below!)

▶️ Watch More Concept Trailers:

Harry Potter and the Cursed Child Trailer - https://youtu.be/OnwogtoNJSA 👈

Frozen: Live Action Movie Trailer -  https://youtu.be/5FlLO5EpNic 👈

Pirates of the Caribbean 6 Trailer - https://youtu.be/uncc9uN0bbI👈

Get ready for the epic conclusion of Netflix's beloved sci-fi horror series with the Stranger Things Season 5 trailer. Set to premiere in November 2025, this final season promises to deliver a thrilling culmination to the Hawkins saga. After delays caused by industry strikes, production wrapped in December 2024, and post-production is ahead of schedule . The Duffer Brothers have crafted an ambitious season described as "eight blockbuster movies," focusing on emotional depth and high-stakes action .

The narrative centers on the Hawkins crew's ultimate battle against Vecna, delving deeper into the mysteries of the Upside Down. Expect a return to the series' roots with a blend of early dynamics and significant character development, particularly highlighting Will's coming-of-age journey . The season will also explore the eerie, time-frozen nature of the Upside Down, potentially incorporating a time jump to align with the aging cast .

The main cast returns, including Millie Bobby Brown, Finn Wolfhard, David Harbour, Winona Ryder, Gaten Matarazzo, Caleb McLaughlin, Noah Schnapp, Sadie Sink, Natalia Dyer, Charlie Heaton, Joe Keery, Maya Hawke, Priah Ferguson, Brett Gelman, Cara Buono, and Jamie Campbell Bower . New additions like Linda Hamilton and Amybeth McNulty join the ensemble, adding fresh dynamics to the story. The eight confirmed episode titles, including "The Crawl," "The Vanishing of…," and "The Rightside Up," hint at a season filled with intrigue and adventure . Don't miss this climactic and nostalgic conclusion to the iconic series.

As derivative works defined under the United States Copyright Act 17 U.S.C. § 101, they may be protected from copyright claims under the fair use doctrine.

The inspiration behind this video: 

Will Eleven get another chance at defeating Vecna? Is Max going to wake up? Can Will ever find peace in his life? These were just some of my biggest questions going into Stranger Things season 5, Volume 1. Seeing as it has been over three years since Stranger Things season 4's ending, my list of lingering questions has become overwhelmingly long. But I guess good things do come to those who wait, because Volume 1's four episodes quickly answer some of my most burning questions.

Set a year and a half after the events of season 4, Stranger Things season 5 finds Hawkins under military control following the "earthquake" that tore apart the town, which was actually caused by Vecna. The villain hasn't been seen since he was thrown from a window with a shotgun blast, but that hasn't stopped the group from staying ready for Vecna's next move. While Hopper and Joyce are helping Eleven train, Mike, Will, Dustin, Lucas, Nancy, Jonathan, Steve, and Robin coordinate ways to locate Vecna. Max is still present, but she remains in a coma, serving as a reminder about how high the stakes are.

Thank You So Much For Watching!
Stay Tuned! Stay Buzzed!

snippet.title: The Incredible World of Completing the Best Game of All Time - Caddicarus
snippet.description:
A love story about Nintendo and a Frenchman. Please make sure you watch in the correct frame rate. ✨✨ GET THE LIMITED BRAND-NEW DVD VERSION OF MY 2022 BLU RAY BOX SET RIGHT HERE = http://pixelempire.com/caddy , along with all of the PS1 box art parodies and poster! ✨✨

Special thanks for this video specifically to...
@Xploshi for the custom theme song variant, @DeadwingDork for the minigames jingle, @AntDude92  and @PeanutButterGamer for their cameos (and Ant again for the Popeye Switch footage), @DidYouKnowGamin's Greg and Dazz for custom DYKGaming intro assets and voice-over cameo (and Greg again for the After Effects help on the Crash face melting scene), @ChannelPup for photoshop assistance (the tower-less NYC skyline and me glued to my bride), The Camera Museum, The Framing Workshop and Oakwood Hall for allowing us to film on location, and i4 Studios in Leeds for the last-minute green screen studio hire while we were up north.


Written, performed and edited entirely by Jim Caddick - with ongoing thanks to... @OllyRoss for filming, @TeeLopes for the intro theme song arrangement, Crisppyboat for the intro video and logo branding (https://twitter.com/CrisppyBoat), Cerys Macaky for her costume/makeup/prop assistance and JetPackBraggin for all of my thumbnails (https://www.twitch.tv/JetPackBraggin).


The Nintendo Switch 2 had one of those new Switch 2 games called Nintendo Switch 2 Welcome Tour, aiming to be the response to Sony's PlayStation 5 games like Astro's Playroom PS5 and Astro Bot PS5 - not because of all the Astro Bot PS5 all easter eggs and Nintendo easter eggs and Nintendo references, but because Welcome Tour review goes out of its way to show everyone with Nintendo Switch 2 Welcome Tour gameplay every new feature of the Switch 2 - which were mostly already shown in the Nintendo Direct Switch 2 reveal and Switch 2 console trailer, but now we have a new Switch 2 game review to play in order to see it for ourselves. We're all hoping for some of the best games of all time and the best games ever made with the new Switch 2 games but we're also likely going to get some of the worst games of all time and even perhaps the worst games ever made with this Nintendo new console leak. Join Caddy through a documentary video, and not a Nintendo documentary exploring Nintendo history documentary, but specifically looking into the history and legacy of frame rates. What is a frame rate and what is the best frame rate possible - I don't know - but hopefully we can all answer what is frame rate and what is a frame rate while exploring frame rates explained, or frame rate explained - which Caddy has gone out of his way to do. There will be Nintendo mini games and not even in a Top 10 Nintendo format, we will be looking at one of everyone's new favorite games for this console. Going from Louis Le Prince and Roundhay Garden Scene to Switch 2 Welcome Tour gameplay with Guess the Frame Rate, going from the first film ever made or the earliest film ever made all the way to Switch 2 Welcome Tour all minigames and Nintendo minigames - get ready to be amazed and saddened by the story of the history of video cameras with a new mockumentary mixed with Switch 2 Welcome Tour all stamps and testing your knowledge with Nintendo Switch 2 Welcome Tour final quiz - don't come to here for any of the Welcome Tour quiz answers though because you won't get anything - but you will know all about frame rates, especially for the Switch 2 frame rate and Switch 2 refresh rate, and then top it off with the new information that the Switch 2 Joy Cons have a new mouse mode with the Switch 2 Joycons new mouse mode. And don't forget that I'm friends with Scott the Woz on Nintendo Online and you aren't.

snippet.description:
Young Jonn and Rema team up for the December hit of 2025 with “Lalala,” the second single off Blue Disco. This feel good anthem is made for fine girls everywhere and for the lovers who hype their girls because they know they look so good.

With infectious melodies, smooth vocals, and that unmistakable December energy, “Lalala” is the soundtrack for good vibes, outside moments, and everyone feeling themselves this season.

Sooner:  https://YoungJonn.lnk.to/sooner
Jiggy Forever : https://YoungJonn.lnk.to/jiggyforever
Love Is Not Enough: https://youngjonn.lnk.to/LINEcc

About Young Jonn
John Saviours Udomboso, fondly known as Young Jonn "The Wicked Producer" is an award winning Afro-pop producer, singer/songwriter. Dubbed the Sound of the Streets, "Young Jonn" is the head huncho and musical genius behind some of the most memorable Artists that own the streets in the Street-Hop or Pop genre. With over 3 awards in some of the prestigious Awards in Nigeria, Young Jonn's sound, lyrics and beats have broken several legendary Artists on the Nigerian music scene since the mid-2000s.  Young Jonn's credits have established him as one of the most iconic producers in the last 10 years. Young Jonn signed an Artist Recording Agreement with Nigeria's foremost record label, Chocolate City with the aim to transition from being a producer to a Recording Artist. His first project Love Is Not Enough was released in the April 2022. In 2024, he released his long-awaited debut album, Jiggy Forever. The album boasts of anthems like Big Big Things, Aquafina, Sharpally, and Stronger.

Subscribe to Young Jonn's channel for all the best and latest official music videos, albums, behind the scenes, live performances and more!

Disney's Zootropolis 2 is finally here, after a long campaign of trailers that didn't particularly catch my eye. Sounds like another basic Disney sequel, as unimpactful as the last few Disney releases. But perhaps I was wrong! After all, the world of Zootopia 1 is one of Disney's most fascinating fantasy worlds to explore, and this 2nd movie certainly does a lot of exploring. But how well it do the second time around? And does the quality of the writing in the narrative, comedy, and concept hold up? Well, here's certainly all of our thoughts, as we review Disney's Zootopia 2.

snippet.title: [Official Trailer] Beside The Sky ต้นฟ้าไต้ฝุ่น | STUDIO WABI SABI
snippet.description:
Beside The Sky | ต้นฟ้าไต้ฝุ่น

ชีวิตของ "ไต้ฝุ่น" ที่ต้องหมุนไปหมุนมาอยู่ในวงโคจรของความเจ็บปวด การถูกทอดทิ้ง และไม่มีใครต้องการ เมื่อได้รับการดูแลจากใครสักคนจึงเป็นเรื่องที่แสนพิเศษ แต่ไต้ฝุ่นเองก็ไม่รู้จะทำอย่างไรให้ "ต้นฟ้า" ทราบว่าเขาได้กอดเก็บเอาความพิเศษนั้นไว้ในส่วนลึกของหัวใจตลอดมา

ทุกวันพฤหัสบดี เวลา 20.30 น. เริ่มตอนแรก 18 ธันวาคม 2568
ดูเวอร์ชัน UNCUT บนแอป WeTV ที่เดียวเท่านั้น

นำแสดงโดย
บีเวอร์ พรรษพล เจนสรรพกิจกุล
ต้นหลิว เมธาพัฒน์ ฉิมกุล
โอ๊ต ธาราธร พุ่มโพธิงาม
เงิน อนุภาษ เหลืองสดใส
พาย ศรัณวุฒิ นิตยสุทธิ
กอล์ฟ พสธร เลิศสถิตย์วงศ์
เอิร์ธ กัษมนณัฏฐ์ นามวิโรจน์ 
ปอนด์ พลวิชญ์ เกตุประภากร
บาส หัสณัฐ พินิวัตร์
แม็กกี้ รชต พิเชฐโชติ

#BesideTheSky #BesideTheSkyTrailer
#FoureverYouProjectPart2 #WeTVth #StudioWabiSabi

Chestnuts roasting on an open fire,
Jack Frost nipping at your nose,
Yuletide carols being sung by a choir
And folks dressed up like eskimos.
 
Everybody knows a turkey and some mistletoe
Help to make the season bright.
Tiny tots with their eyes all aglow
Will find it hard to sleep tonight.
They know that Santa's on his way
He's loaded lots of toys and goodies on his sleigh
And ev'rymother's child is gonna spy
To see if reindeer really know how to fly.
 
And so I'm offering this simple phrase
To kids from one to ninety-two
Although its been said many times,
Many ways: "Merry Christmas to you"
